Subject: Re: RE: [VB] Flip seat Westy/ M code help

SK might be taken from the name Sikkens, but it doesn't come from "special kolour". Those two words don't exist in the german language. Special in German is "Sonder" and color is "Farbe", so a special color would be a sonderfarbe.

John
'65 Deluxe
'65 Crewcab

